OL,3,CPepper spray to be introduced at
OL,4,CFeltham Young Offenders Institution
OL,6,FFeltham Young Offender Institution
OL,7,F(YOI) will be one of three public
OL,8,Fsector institutions where synthetic
OL,9,Fpepper spray is introduced this
OL,10,Fsummer, as part of efforts to combat
OL,11,Frising levels of violence against
OL,12,Fstaff.
OL,14,FThe move comes after new figures
OL,15,Freleased by the Ministry of Justice
OL,16,F(MoJ) on Thursday showed rates of
OL,17,Fassaults on staff were 14 times higher
OL,18,Fthan at adult prisons.
