OL,3,CPepper spray to be introduced at
OL,4,CFeltham Young Offenders Institution
OL,6,FPava spray, already used by police and
OL,7,Fguards in adult prisons, will be
OL,8,Frolled out "in limited circumstances"
OL,9,Fto specialist staff at Feltham A,
OL,10,FWerrington and Wetherby ` the three
OL,11,Fpublic sector YOIs that hold children
OL,12,Funder 18.
OL,14,FStaff at Feltham will receive "a
OL,15,Freally high level" of training and
OL,16,Fthere will be "a very clear, high
OL,17,Fthreshold" for when the spray can be
OL,18,Fused, according to a senior youth
OL,19,Fcustody source.
