OL,3,CPepper spray to be introduced at
OL,4,CFeltham Young Offenders Institution
OL,6,FRecent incidents have left officers at
OL,7,FYOIs with fractures, dislocations and
OL,8,Fpuncture wounds, the MoJ said.
OL,10,FInmates have reportedly used cutlery
OL,11,Fand screws taken from furniture as
OL,12,Fweapons.
OL,14,FIn one case, a female staff member
OL,15,Fused her body as a human shield to
OL,16,Fprotect a child who was being attacked
OL,17,Fin a group assault in the courtyard, a
OL,18,Fsenior source said.
