OL,3,CPepper spray to be introduced at
OL,4,CFeltham Young Offenders Institution
OL,6,FMoJ data shows Feltham had 170.0
OL,7,Fassaults on staff per 100 children and
OL,8,Fyoung people last year. This compares
OL,9,Fto 182.9 at Werrington and 167.4 at
OL,10,FWetherby.
OL,12,FAcross the whole of the children and
OL,13,Fyoung persons secure estate `
OL,14,Fincluding other establishments such as
OL,15,Fsecure children's homes ` the rate of
OL,16,Fassaults on staff was 183.6 per 100, a
OL,17,Fslight drop from 187.2 in 2023.
