OL,3,CPepper spray to be introduced at
OL,4,CFeltham Young Offenders Institution
OL,6,FJustice minister Sir Nic Dakin said:
OL,7,F"This government inherited a criminal
OL,8,Fjustice system in crisis. The
OL,9,Funacceptable levels of violence faced
OL,10,Fby our brave frontline officers in
OL,11,Fyoung offender institutions is yet
OL,12,Fanother symptom of that.
OL,14,F"This is not a decision we have made
OL,15,Flightly, but our overarching duty is
OL,16,Fto keep staff and young people in
OL,17,Fcustody safe. This spray is a vital
OL,18,Ftool to prevent serious violence,
OL,19,Fhelping staff to focus on
OL,20,Frehabilitation as part of our Plan for
OL,21,FChange."
