OL,3,CPepper spray to be introduced at
OL,4,CFeltham Young Offenders Institution
OL,6,FThe rollout will last 12 months and be
OL,7,Freviewed by ministers. Each use of the
OL,8,Fspray will also be assessed by an
OL,9,Findependent panel.
OL,11,FYouth justice charity the Howard
OL,12,FLeague for Penal Reform has condemned
OL,13,Fthe move.
