OL,3,CPepper spray to be introduced at
OL,4,CFeltham Young Offenders Institution
OL,6,FAndrea Coomber KC, the charity's chief
OL,7,Fexecutive, said: "There is too much
OL,8,Fviolence in prisons holding children,
OL,9,Fbut this is a direct consequence of a
OL,10,Ffailing system that keeps boys as
OL,11,Fyoung as 15 locked in their cells for
OL,12,Fup to 23 hours a day without
OL,13,Fmeaningful access to education or
OL,14,Fsocial interaction.
OL,16,F"It reflects a profound failure on the
OL,17,Fpart of those responsible for children
OL,18,Fin custody that they would consider
OL,19,Fintroducing weapons in the name of
OL,20,Fsafety.
OL,26,@oD@ROUxD@AOU
