OL,3,CPepper spray to be introduced at
OL,4,CFeltham Young Offenders Institution
OL,6,F"Instead of arming staff, the way to
OL,7,Freduce violence is to close failing
OL,8,Fyoung offender institutions and ensure
OL,9,Fthat children are accommodated in more
OL,10,Fappropriate settings - such as secure
OL,11,Fchildren's homes - where they can be
OL,12,Fgiven the care and support they need.
OL,14,F"Prison is no place for a child."
OL,16,FThe move was welcomed by the Prison
OL,17,FOfficers' Association.
