OL,6,FSteve Gillan, general secretary of the
OL,7,FPOA, said: "Young offenders
OL,8,Finstitutions can be a very challenging
OL,9,Fenvironment for our members to work in.
OL,11,F"Prison officers must be given the
OL,12,Fright PPE to protect themselves and
OL,13,Fprisoners from violence. This is a
OL,14,Fstep in the right direction."
